          We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms at any time. If a revision is material, 
          we will provide notice prior to any new terms taking effect.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="contact-info">
          <strong>Kinevra</strong><br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:daniel@kinevra.com">daniel@kinevra.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 60px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .legal-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .legal-content {
    padding: 40px 0 100px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin: 40px 0 20px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .content-wrapper h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .content-wrapper ul {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .content-wrapper li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-wrapper {
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
